{"tid":1592683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好啦!!!係時候講返 927 928 929 101 四次活動 + 支線活動","createTime":"2019-09-24T17:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T09:40:34.000Z","uid":94771,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"91819cefafa2d59f2a376c275d05e0d2db131834","tid":1592683,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:19:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>文宣方面</strong><br />\n我地已經無佐 6,7月的的規模啦<br />\n所以派傳單 放映會要重開 而且為鼓勵人多做<br />\n被破壞的連濃牆要重新光復<br />\n我建議做的時候可以上來連登拎光環 鼓舞士氣<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有關活動實際做法</strong><br />\n928 929 101 <strong>依三日完全無討論應該咩性質 再唔討論就無啦</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>927 基本上和理非</strong><br />\n<br />\n928  晚上7至9 基本上咁的時間即係民陣可能都唔會大搞啦 當然其他手足有咩諗法再講<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tP6B2CW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtP6B2CW.jpg&h=0e3d1b25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>929 全球反#Chinazi</strong><br />\n請手足幫忙做Twitter攻勢 另外香港無咩人知929做咩，要幫手做文宣<br />\n<strong>另外依一日係和理非定勇武　上場都好多人討論而無共識</strong><br />\n又人話因為國際Connect日 所以要和理非 有人又話唔同意 <strong>所以大家要繼續討論</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yXtTNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yXtTNL.jpg&h=1379875d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>101國殯日</strong><br />\n依一日唔需要講 一定係會勇武大搞架啦<br />\n問題來啦 係港島搞怕比人圍捕 但各區又無象徵性<br />\n所以全人港島定各區到而家都無共識<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我個人建議就係勇武去各區 和理非去港島的</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LqtQnF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLqtQnF9.jpg&h=3fc8c972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一方面 支線已經幾乎無啦<br />\n紙鶴活動 <strong>之前有人話一齊做 再掛係唔同地方無佐回事</strong><br />\n唱完歌 <strong>有人話會拉隊去搞牆 一樣無咩人做</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>星期三啦 唔好再做偵探啦</strong> 有D野比你估中 對面死唔認你都無計架 你轉唔到做核彈架<br />\n所以依三日連登仔一定要返返6,7月風氣 全部行動POST"},{"pid":"79796089dfe49a19b03ba6fb83ed2cb4ace70a72","tid":1592683,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"224de7569c048de952730813c1bd59384ad1a6e2","tid":1592683,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a3c75357022a9181abdba7be68927dd01b1f86","tid":1592683,"uid":261530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58d76ca89ec80ce68b74e71c7ec1f453144e0672","tid":1592683,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:31:20.000Z","msg":"[文宣] 我哋好似忘記咗其中一條重要戰線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592692</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b8cfb1967c63a78465e4c6f85602b32108daadf7","tid":1592683,"uid":200554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:49:16.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"ae1a07c04bba45c6a31b446febeb4e11bc487863","tid":1592683,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T23:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"958a166b9a11bb583b873541240f4f0b508c7e02","tid":1592683,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T00:02:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.27 聲援被捕者集會<br />\n9.28 反抗威權 迎接黎明<br />\n9.29 全球反極權大遊行<br />\n10.1 沒有國慶 只有國殤<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n我要真普選<br />\n</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icLSUe6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicLSUe6.jpg&h=1a52e068&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c140122f916a7fe0ec94a8d212a4dd4e038a95f1","tid":1592683,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6c0d8dfbf9b67850db2bc007612cd96de20b8b4","tid":1592683,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e2aba08f3b1859f04ac5b38e1a56919cf0ef86f","tid":1592683,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:31:39.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=979f8b65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=TCbK1UWcamxL4EXsadWaUuu9cyR3gY7uP1sO3WVLDIg%3D&h=aeecab00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RcHaJTs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcHaJTs.jpg&h=032e94ee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OWfr1E9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOWfr1E9.jpg&h=defd0334&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mdP4Oj9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmdP4Oj9.jpg&h=386586b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d7oECdw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd7oE